"privacy_title" = "Privacy Policy";
"privacy_intro_title" = "Introduction";
"privacy_intro_body" = "This Privacy Policy explains how MyPlanet Lite, offered through your organization, handles personal data when you use the app.";
"privacy_collect_title" = "Information we collect";
"privacy_collect_body" = "We collect:\n• Account data (name, username, email, organization).\n• Usage and diagnostic information (session activity, feature interactions, device and app version).\n• Optional content you submit (posts, survey responses, media files).";
"privacy_use_title" = "How we use your information";
"privacy_use_body" = "We use the data to provide core features, sync learning content, personalize language and regional settings, improve performance and reliability, and support security, fraud prevention, and investigations.";
"privacy_storage_title" = "Storage and retention";
"privacy_storage_body" = "Information is stored on secure servers managed by OLE or your organization with access controls and encryption in transit. We retain data only as long as needed to provide the service, meet legal requirements, enforce agreements, or resolve disputes, with limited retention for backups.";
"privacy_share_title" = "Sharing and third parties";
"privacy_share_body" = "We do not sell personal data. Information may be shared with trusted service providers (e.g., hosting, analytics, or notifications) under data protection agreements, with your organization’s administrators to manage accounts, or when required by law.";
"privacy_rights_title" = "Your choices and rights";
"privacy_rights_body" = "You can review or update your profile data in the app. Where applicable, you may request access, rectification, deletion, restriction, or portability of your data, or object to certain processing. You may withdraw optional data by deleting that content or stopping submission.";
"privacy_security_title" = "Security";
"privacy_security_body" = "We apply technical and organizational measures such as encryption in transit (TLS), authentication controls, least-privilege access, and monitoring to reduce the risk of unauthorized access or disclosure. Keep your credentials safe.";
"privacy_children_title" = "Children’s data";
"privacy_children_body" = "The app is intended for learners authorized through partner organizations. If a child’s data was collected without required consent, contact us to remove it.";
"privacy_updates_title" = "Policy updates";
"privacy_updates_body" = "We may update this policy to reflect product, security, or legal changes. Material updates will be communicated through in-app notices or other appropriate channels.";
"privacy_contact_title" = "Contact";
"privacy_contact_body" = "For questions or to exercise your privacy rights, contact your organization’s administrator or our support team.";
